high_descs: Walk towards the stove counter
Grab a knife from the counter
Walk towards the island counter
Slice the lettuce on the counter
Turn right and walk towards the trash can
Put the knife in the trash can
Walk towards the counter
Grab a slice of lettuce from the counter
Walk with the lettuce slice towards the sink
Put the lettuce slice in the sink, open the water, close it and take the lettuce slice
Walk with the lettuce slice towards the stove counter
Put the lettuce slice on the counter
anns.task_desc: Slice the lettuce, grab a slice,  rinse it in the sink, put it in the counter

high_descs: Turn around and move to stand at the counter between the stove and sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Turn back around and move to the end of the kitchen island to stand in front of the head of lettuce so the window is at your back.
Slice the head of lettuce with the knife.
Turn around to face the trash bin, which is by the window.
Place the knife in the trash bin.
Turn back around to face the lettuce again.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the kitchen island.
Carry the slice of lettuce to the sink.
Place the lettuce in the right side of the sink, turn on the water, and then remove the lettuce once washed.
Carry the lettuce to your left to stand at the counter space between the trash bin and the stove.
Place the lettuce on the counter left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed slice of lettuce on the counter by the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter beside the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn around and face the kitchen island on the left.
Slice up the lettuce.
Turn around to the trashcan.
Place the knife in the trashcan.
Turn back around to face the island.
Grab a slice of lettuce.
Turn left and walk back to the sink and face it.
Place the lettuce in the left sink and rinse it off.
Turn around and face the counter space beside the stove.
Place the lettuce on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed lettuce slice on the counter next to the stove.
